# SOC Case Study â€” Splunk Multi-Platform Log Analysis

This project demonstrates practical SOC analysis using Splunk to monitor, analyze, and visualize security logs from multiple platforms including Apache Web Server, MacOS, Linux, Health App, and OpenSSH server environments.

---

## ðŸŽ¯ Project Objectives
- Centralize log data from diverse systems
- Detect anomalies, brute-force attacks, and unauthorized activities
- Build dashboards for real-time monitoring
- Compare Splunk with alternative SIEM/log analysis tools
- Provide mitigation recommendations to improve security posture

