## ðŸ” Log Sources Analyzed
| Log Source | Key Use Case |
|-----------|--------------|
| **Apache Web Server** | Traffic monitoring & threat geolocation |
| **MacOS System Logs** | Hardware/USB activity, Wi-Fi abuse |
| **Linux Logs** | Service failures, suspicious network connections |
| **Health App Logs** | Data integrity & unusual behavior detection |
| **OpenSSH Server Logs** | SSH brute-force attack identification |

